parameters: \nc<Doctor>I'm afraid I have some difficult news to convey...
\nc<Doctor>It seems that your race has changed.
\nc<Saki>Is... is such a thing even possible?

\nc<Doctor>Your body has completely transformed into that of a demon...
specifically, a succubus.
\bustMsgExpression[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Then... is there a way to change back...?

\nc<Doctor>There have been no reported cases of a demon turning into a
human. Of course, the reverse is also true.
\nc<Doctor>I'm sorry, but there is nothing our facility can do for you.
